                              Mission Statement
   The mission of the U.S. Probation and Pretrial Services Office for the
   Southern District of Indiana is to provide protection to the community
      while imparting quality service in the administration of justice.
                                 Core Aims:
                  Empower and encourage employees to reach
                    their maximum professional potential.
                 Consistently strive to improve the quality
                    of our products and services through
                          teamwork and cooperation.
              Promote and maintain a positive work environment
                  built on professionalism, mutual respect,
                       open communication, and trust.
